{"tid":1041152,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[餃子狂想曲] 辣雞麵雞肉餃子","createTime":"2019-02-28T15:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T04:15:04.000Z","uid":133911,"like":90,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b078c083c3ded9e192e0843d78841c3e12ec25","tid":1041152,"uid":133911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"喂大家好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2019年第一個post，我決定包啲特別啲嘅餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係<br />\n將啲辣雞麵包落啲餃子入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n適逢咁啱轉咗工，識到班癲癲地嘅同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見有人last day，佢哋又好支持我對餃子嘅創意<br />\n所以我決定將今次嘅創意！送比我今日last day嘅同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GgP2mb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GgP2mb.png&h=48fa81c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6tfdsS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6tfdsS.png&h=ae060364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSorly又係你哋好憎嘅泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原諒我下次唔落<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MkdKzy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MkdKzy.png&h=8893500a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲泡菜同啲雞肉撈埋成pat咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyVM4zz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyVM4zz.png&h=08b234ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AUdF81f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAUdF81f.png&h=a1731599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upXcfGh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupXcfGh.png&h=6a5e6056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQVxfGh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQVxfGh.png&h=5689c775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為淨麵我怕太單調，所以有啲係加咗雞肉，另一啲係淨麵/淨雞肉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cetu2mi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcetu2mi.png&h=6df4b425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包完個樣都幾似樣，我估應該冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW後面朵花幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScSPhXg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScSPhXg.png&h=22bfbf80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係葱花呀！<br />\n<br />\n包完之後我就雪咗落冷格，等到今日拎返公司蒸熟同同事分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQRwwhL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQRwwhL.png&h=a9b33b05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rV9J6Q7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrV9J6Q7.png&h=b8e69352&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6J83npt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6J83npt.png&h=48df41d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泡菜雞肉餃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L44Vdwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL44Vdwa.png&h=5304ed8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬眾期待嘅辣雞麵餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同事1點評 (雞肉麵餃)<br />\n個麵味道比較淡，如果有個醬或者豉油點下可能好啲，但個外型幾好<br />\n<br />\n同事2點評 (雞肉麵餃)<br />\n(面容扭曲) 都幾辣下，個口感有少少奇怪咁<br />\n<br />\n同事3點評 (麵餃)<br />\n佢表示鍾意試伏，食得好開心，亦冇留下任何comment<br />\n<br />\n真。last day同事點評 (麵餃)<br />\n(試完第一啖表情複雜) ....嗯<br />\n<br />\n然後唔知邊條蛋散話，不如比老闆試下味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好死唔死老闆又真係行過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係咁<br />\n佢就食咗最後一粒餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆點評 (雞餃)<br />\n個皮有少少厚，不過現成皮係咁架喇，個味都幾ok吖，個樣幾靚<br />\n<br />\n好撚彩啲同事之前食晒啲麵餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係下個月嘅今日就會係我嘅last day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df2c5b09bae4004ada37ea92e3a41945c2cd024","tid":1041152,"uid":76375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />餓了"},{"pid":"bdfcf0f3dbe82bcde71d96290fa1adb9873674fd","tid":1041152,"uid":114738,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"睇得出絲打對餃子好有愛 次次都係餃子實驗<br />\n下個臧姑娘仲唔係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好葡萄你可以係office有人咁樣溫馨地一齊癲!!! 將紅同白獻畀同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb59a98ea3cc3c4a0b3f687a7885df85b3dc989e","tid":1041152,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"呢個牌子自己有出餃子喎"},{"pid":"43792b56b83b34606f6bafefadc394f9320cb270","tid":1041152,"uid":154879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"咁整餃子幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有其他創意餃"},{"pid":"a03b6c2c030ebb7a34edfc23d81452e4d2ce287f","tid":1041152,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"幾時再整啲甜餃"},{"pid":"0afb358d1f76cf343c7e3489bac7cae2f5c8c275","tid":1041152,"uid":133911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6df2c5b09bae4004ada37ea92e3a41945c2cd024","tid":1041152,"uid":76375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />餓了"},"citedBy