9","tid":1041152,"uid":10984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"我都好中意食餃子 我又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"聽朝食餃子做早餐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818ae01b5989eae4456b86ca6862c9efecb22417","tid":1041152,"uid":133911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f5a60db176cdf90b99c7fd3a41c03a7e9dc7da3","tid":1041152,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"炒飯餃應該好食過麵餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次要試下炒飯先得<br />\n不過有少少驚炒飯做餡會太乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2693af01dc64c589d47c47929778ea45c0b2261","tid":1041152,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"小短腿又出現為禍餃子界🥟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}